The spec trail is pointing away from “D3D11 omits w clipping”: D3D11 explicitly requires `0 < w` clipping even when depth clipping is disabled. I’m doing one last pass for app-level clip-plane and transformed-vertex usage so the repo divergence list is complete rather than just the default state blocks.
